"\">Syllable</a>, just to name a few."
msgstr ""
"Parmi eux, on trouvera les dérivés UNIX <a href=\"http://freebsd.org/"
"\">FreeBSD</a>, <a href=\"http://netbsd.org/\">NetBSD</a>, <a href=\"http://"
"openbsd.org/\">OpenBSD</a> and <a href=\"http://opensolaris.org/"
"\">OpenSolaris</a>, le clone BeOS <a href=\"http://haiku-os.org/\">Haiku OS</"
"a>, le clone Windows NT <a href=\"http://reactos.sf.net/\">ReactOS</a>, le "
"clone DOS <a href=\"http://www.freedos.org/\">FreeDOS</a>, <a href=\"http://"
